    public class ResettableEventTokenMatcher
extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseMatcher<ResettableEventTokenMatch>
    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.engine.runtime.resettableEventToken pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as ResettableEventTokenMatch.

    Original source: 

     pattern resettableEventToken(automaton : Automaton, eventToken : EventToken){
        neg find tokenInInitState(automaton, eventToken);
        neg find tokenInFinalState(automaton, eventToken);
 }
    See Also:
    ResettableEventTokenMatch, ResettableEventTokenProcessor, ResettableEventTokenQuerySpecification
